    <title>The 2012 Strike in Québec: Full Report</title>
    <link>http://www.crimethinc.com/blog/2012/08/14/the-2012-strike-in-quebec-full-report/</link>
    <pubDate>Wed, 15 Aug 2012 05:17:53 +0000</pubDate>
